<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link href="~/lib/font-awesome/css/all.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .event-info {
            margin: auto;
            width: 80%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 25px;
        }

            .event-info p {
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }

                .event-info p span {
                    display: inline-block;
                    margin: 5px;
                    padding: 5px 10px;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    background-color: azure;
                    color: lightgray;
                }

        .button {
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .glow-on-hover {
            width: 35%;
            margin-right: 30px;
            height: auto;
            min-height: 100px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: #111;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 30px;
            z-index: 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

            .glow-on-hover:before {
                content: '';
                background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff0000, #ff7300, #fffb00, #48ff00, #00ffd5, #002bff, #7a00ff, #ff00c8, #ff0000);
                position: absolute;
                top: -2px;
                left: -2px;
                background-size: 400%;
                z-index: -1;
                filter: blur(5px);
                width: calc(100% + 4px);
                height: calc(100% + 4px);
                animation: glowing 20s linear infinite;
                opacity: 0;
                transition: opacity .3s ease-in-out;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .glow-on-hover:active {
                color: #000
            }

                .glow-on-hover:active:after {
                    background: transparent;
                }

            .glow-on-hover:hover:before {
                opacity: 1;
            }

            .glow-on-hover:after {
                z-index: -1;
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                background: #ED3A85;
                left: 0;
                top: 0;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        @@keyframes glowing {
            0% {
                background-position: 0 0;
            }

            50% {
                background-position: 400% 0;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 0 0;
            }
        }

        .reviews {
            margin: auto;
            width: 80%;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .review-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid lightgray;
        }

            .review-item:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }

        .review-name {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .review-rating {
            color: orange;
        }

        .review-description {
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="event-info">
        <h1>Event Name</h1>
        <p>Event Date: <span class="value">Event Date Value</span></p>
        <p>Event Place: <span class="value">Event Place Value</span></p>
        <p>Event Description: <span class="value">Event Description Value</span></p>
        <p>Ticket Price (Normal): <span class="value">Ticket Price (Normal) Value</span></p>
        <p>Ticket Price (Reduced): <span class="value">Ticket Price (Reduced) Value</span></p>
        <p>Event Category: <span class="value">Event Category Value</span></p>
        <p>Available Seats: <span class="value">Available Seats Value</span></p>
        <p>Event Start Time: <span class="value">Event Start Time Value</span></p>
        <p>Target Audience: <span class="value">Target Audience Value</span></p>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <button class="glow-on-hover" type="button">Buy a reduced ticket</button>
        <button class="glow-on-hover" type="button">Buy a normal ticket</button>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews">
        <h2>Event Reviews</h2>
        <div class="review-item">
            <div class="review-name">John Doe</div>
            <div class="review-rating">Rating: 8/10</div>
            <div class="review-description">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis ultrices gravida dapibus.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-item">
            <div class="review-name">Jane Smith</div>
            <div class="review-rating">Rating: 9/10</div>
            <div class="review-description">Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-item">
            <div class="review-name">David Johnson</div>
            <div class="review-rating">Rating: 7/10</div>
            <div class="review-description">Fusce fringilla erat eu dolor mattis, sed aliquet leo lacinia.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
